  "abstract": "The Canada Lands Survey System (CLSS) Administrative Boundaries web service includes legislative boundaries of Aboriginal Lands, National Parks of Canada and National Park Reserves of Canada.  More specifically it includes, but is not limited to, Indian Reserves, Cree-Naskapi Category 1A and 1A-N Lands, Gwich’in Lands, Kanesatake Mohawk Interim Land Base, Inuvialuit Lands, the Inuit Owned Lands, Sechelt Lands, Salt River First Nation Settlement Lands, Sahtu Lands, Tlicho Lands and Yukon First Nation Settlement Lands.",
